Just suffered several tough weeks, sorry for the late PR.

I have tested the mxnet-spark on EC2 g2 & c4 instances, which works well. As I mentioned in README.md, there still exists some pitfalls which we need to solve in the future. I'll also open another issue to list all these problems and make a roadmap.

@liyuance Tech manager of Qihoo 360's infrastructure team, is willing to deploy MXNet on Spark on their  Yarn clusters. He gave quite a lot of suggestion during my development.
